        "Curriculum boss battles",
        "Advanced teaching templates"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Clan Leadership & Skool Community",
      "purpose": "Community building, engagement, moderation, and member value.",
      "progressDefinition": "Consistent posts, challenges, and member wins.",
